\cos(u+v) = \cos u \cos v - \sin u \sin v
u = \phi
v = \pi/2
\cos(\phi+\pi/2) = \cos \phi \cos \pi/2 - \sin \phi \sin \pi / 2 = 0 - 1\cdot \sin \phi
